Car Management:
Add new car entries to the system.
Edit existing car information (details, images, availability, price).
Delete car entries from the system (when no longer available).

User Management:
View a list of registered users.
Option to edit or delete user accounts (for exceptional cases).

Booking Management:
View a comprehensive list of all booking requests.
Manage booking statuses (e.g., confirmed, pending, canceled).

Reports & Analytics (Optional):
Generate reports on bookings, revenue, and user activity.
View insights into user preferences and rental trends.